    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Annelise lives in the year 2100.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a burning flame, one morning like many others, she glimpses a female figure absolutely identical to her. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063900/extras/5886b5172c83eec75a9b035b398c93b4.avif?t=1751716386\" width=500 height=280 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From that moment her life will change. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She'll have to know why she can see the other her but she can't speak to her.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She'll have to search for informations on ancient tomes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She'll have to solve puzzles and pass trials.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She'll have to learn how to harness ancient powers. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And in the meantime she will learn about the existence of a prophecy, of an angry Supreme God, of the arrival of Four Plagues dooming the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She will understand to be part of something totally unexpected and too big for her to manage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>And that somewhere in time, she is not alone.</strong></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063900/extras/cbc84643bb52ee2fbc1ad03c0675969e.avif?t=1751716386\" width=500 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join Annelise in her quest to get and empower the epic Pyrite Talisman.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Break the barrier of time separating Annelise from the other Her and share the knowledge to progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Pyrite Talisman is a 3D narrative adventure involving exploration in third person direct movement, puzzle solving and inventory use through a point &amp; click interface and it's the prequel to Telluria: Forebodings. During gameplay you will play with both characters switching through time to collect informations to progress further into the story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Subtitles and interface in english and italian.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow the Telluria project on our socials.</p>",
